EZDownloader - Source Code
==========================

Download videos/audios from Youtube and images from internet (not so cool) following easy steps!
If you don't know how to use it, execute '--help' to see all the available commands.

The objective is download files from Youtube in a simple way, without needing to access websites to do it. All by cmd.

Current functionalities
  - Save a default path for automate the download proccess. (--set-path)
  - Download Youtube video/audio in the specified location (default or not).
  - Download images from internet in the specified location (default or not) - (Don't use it, I just did it for fun. Downloading directly is faster...).


Still with some problems, so... still in work.
